This page is a list of one-word [[message]]s.

== Sound effects ==

"Boing!" &ndash; A creature with [[magic resistance]] was hit by a [[wand of striking]] or spell of {{spell of|force bolt}}.{{refsrc|src/zap.c|166|nethack=3.6.7}}{{refsrc|src/zap.c|2284|nethack=3.6.7}}{{refsrc|src/muse.c|1253|nethack=3.6.7}}{{refsrc|src/muse.c|1266|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Splat!" &ndash; An [[egg]] or [[melon]] broke. Could be due to throwing it, or it being destroyed by a force bolt or wand of striking while in inventory.{{refsrc|src/dothrow.c|2105|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Splash!" &ndash; [[Venom]] was thrown.{{refsrc|src/dothrow.c|2113|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Crash!" &ndash; A [[potion]] hit a monster that you can't see.{{refsrc|src/potion.c|1345|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Whang!" &ndash; A [[boulder]] or [[iron ball]] hit [[iron bars]].{{refsrc|src/mthrowu.c|1146|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Clink!" &ndash; [[Gold]] hit iron bars.{{refsrc|src/mthrowu.c|1150|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Clonk!" &ndash; Some other kind of thrown object hit iron bars.{{refsrc|src/mthrowu.c|1152|nethack=3.6.7}}

== Player actions ==

=== Kicking ===

"Thwwpingg! &ndash; You [[kick]]ed a pile of gold and sent some of them flying.{{refsrc|src/dokick.c|663|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Thump!" &ndash; You [[kick]]ed a pile of gold larger than 300 zorkmids and none of them went flying.{{refsrc|src/dokick.c|671||nethack=3.6.7}}

"THUD!" &ndash; You [[kick]]ed a [[large box]] or a [[chest]] and it did not move because it is either too heavy or against a wall.{{refsrc|src/dokick.c|615|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Thump!" &ndash; You [[kick]]ed some other object, but the object did not move because it is either too heavy or against a wall.{{refsrc|src/dokick.c|649|nethack=3.6.7}} If a [[gray stone]] is not against the wall, then "Thump!" identifies it as a [[loadstone]].

"Klunk!" &ndash; You kicked a [[sink]] and you are deaf.{{refsrc|src/dokick.c|1175|nethack=3.6.7}} 

"WHAMMM!!!" &ndash; You kicked a [[door]], but it didn't break.{{refsrc|src/dokick.c|1315|nethack=3.6.7}}

=== Dropping ===

"Splash!" &ndash; You dropped a heavy object ([[weight]] 10 or more) into a [[pool]].{{refsrc|src/do.c|239|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Plop!" &ndash; You dropped a light object (weight 9 or less) into a pool while [[levitating]] or [[flying]] over it.{{refsrc|src/do.c|241|nethack=3.6.7}}

=== Locking ===

"Klunk!" &ndash; A spell of {{spell of|wizard lock}} or a [[wand of locking]] [[lock]]ed a [[box]] or a [[chest]].{{refsrc|src/lock.c|884|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Klick!" &ndash; A spell of {{spell of|knock}} or a [[wand of opening]] unlocked a box or a chest.{{refsrc|src/lock.c|897|nethack=3.6.7}}

=== Digging ===

"Clash!" &ndash; You tried to [[dig]] outside the map area with a [[pick-axe]].{{refsrc|src/dig.c|1062|nethack=3.6.7}} (This is possible only if the diggable area of the level extends all the way to the edge of the map.)

"Clang!" &ndash; You tried to dig through [[iron bars]] with a pick-axe.{{refsrc|src/dig.c|1084|nethack=3.6.7}}

=== Teleporting ===

"Sorry..." &ndash; You attempted a [[teleport control|controlled teleport]] into an invalid or unsafe location,{{refsrc|src/teleport.c|533|nethack=3.6.7}} or you attempted to [[level teleport]] into (or below) the [[Sanctum]] before performing the [[invocation]].{{refsrc|src/teleport.c|1009|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Oops..." &ndash; You attempted a controlled level teleport while [[confused]] and ended up on a random level instead.{{refsrc|src/teleport.c|822|nethack=3.6.7}}{{refsrc|src/teleport.c|829|nethack=3.6.7}}

=== Combat ===

"Splash!" &ndash; You hit an eyeless monster with [[blinding venom]], or you hit a monster with blinding venom while you were blind.{{refsrc|src/uhitm.c|1034|nethack=3.6.7}}{{refsrc|src/uhitm.c|1008|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Splat!" &ndash; You hit a monster with an ordinary [[egg]],{{refsrc|src/uhitm.c|984|nethack=3.6.7}} or same as above, but you hit the monster with a [[cream pie]].{{refsrc|src/uhitm.c|1034|nethack=3.6.7}}{{refsrc|src/uhitm.c|1007|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Snap!" &ndash; You [[apply|applied]] a [[bullwhip]] but hit nothing.{{refsrc|src/apply.c|2646|nethack=3.6.7}}

=== Other ===

"Whoops..." &ndash; You failed to [[untrap]] a [[trap]] and just made things worse.{{refsrc|src/trap.c|4093|nethack=3.6.7}}

== Monster noises==

"Surrender!" &ndash; A possible message from an angry [[soldier]].{{refsrc|src/sounds.c|915|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Gleep!" &ndash; A tame baby [[dragon]] hatched from an [[egg]].{{refsrc|src/timeout.c|907|nethack=3.6.7}} This is a reference to the ''[[wikipedia:MythAdventures|MythAdventures]]'' series of books by Robert Asprin.

"Burrrrp!" &ndash; A monster with a [[digestion attack]] swallowed another monster.{{refsrc|src/mhitm.c|921|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Gasp!" / "What?" / "Why?" &ndash; A [[peaceful]] monster saw you attack another peaceful monster.{{refsrc|src/mon.c|2988|nethack=3.6.7}}

=== Chatting ===

"Nevermore!" &ndash; [[Chat]] with a non-[[peaceful]] [[raven]].{{refsrc|src/sounds.c|680|nethack=3.6.7}} This is a reference to Edgar Allan Poe's poem "[[wikipedia:The Raven|The Raven]]".

"Huh?" / "What?" / "Eh?" &ndash; Chat with a [[stunned]] or [[confused]] peaceful [[humanoid]].{{refsrc|src/sounds.c|785|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Aloha." &ndash; Chat with a peaceful [[tourist (player monster)|tourist]].{{refsrc|src/sounds.c|833|nethack=3.6.7}}

=== Mail daemon ===

"Gangway!" &ndash; A message the [[mail daemon]] says when pushing monsters out of its way.{{refsrc|src/mail.c|274|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Catch!" &ndash; The mail daemon can't reach you, so it throws the [[scroll of mail]] at you.{{refsrc|src/mail.c|417|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Oops!" &ndash; You failed to pick up the scroll of mail for some reason, e.g. because you [[fumble]]d or because your [[inventory]] was full.{{refsrc|src/mail.c|419|nethack=3.6.7}}

== Miscellaneous ==

"Ouch!" &ndash; You [[hurtle]]d into a [[wall]], a [[door]], or a [[tree]].{{refsrc|src/dothrow.c|603|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Yuck!" &ndash; A [[green slime]] touched you and [[slime]]d you when you were already slimed; this has no effect.{{refsrc|src/mhitu.c|1652|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Cheapskate." &ndash; You offered too little gold to an [[aligned priest]].{{refsrc|src/priest.c|603|nethack=3.6.7}}

"Interesting..." &ndash; You [[dip]]ped something to no effect.{{refsrc|src/potion.c|2287|nethack=3.6.7}}

